{"sha": "e4c64a1499de8a14a34f77c844b7fc1f7cabffd6", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOmU0YzY0YTE0OTlkZThhMTRhMzRmNzdjODQ0YjdmYzFmN2NhYmZmZDY=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2015-05-27T00:42:55Z"}, "committer": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2015-05-27T00:42:55Z"}, "message": "Auto merge of #25713 - Stebalien:pattern, r=alexcrichton\n\nNeeded to support:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nmatch X {\r\n  pattern if Y ...\r\n}\r\n\r\nfor pattern in Y {}\r\n```\r\n\r\nIMO, this shouldn't require an RFC because it can't interfere with any future language changes (because `pattern if` and `pattern in` are already legal in rust) and can't cause any ambiguity.", "tree": {"sha": "2aeabe631438fae6ebc399979adae243360a7322", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/2aeabe631438fae6ebc399979adae243360a7322"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/e4c64a1499de8a14a34f77c844b7fc1f7cabffd6", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/e4c64a1499de8a14a34f77c844b7fc1f7cabffd6", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/e4c64a1499de8a14a34f77c844b7fc1f7cabffd6", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/e4c64a1499de8a14a34f77c844b7fc1f7cabffd6/comments", "author": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.githu